basic.floral_language:
Anthurium crystallinum
Anthurium crystallinumFloriography: enthusiastic, bright, bold and unrestrained 
Anthurium crystallinumis one of the world precious flowers, cultivated from the flower kingdom of the Netherlands. 
Anthurium crystallinumflower such as fire, red bud is like a palm, tassel graceful palm a golden yellow flesh, vividly called spathe. Because of their enthusiasm is bold and unrestrained individual character, events like wedding or new store opening, choosing it as decoration, increase the festive atmosphere. 
Anthurium crystallinummaintenance is simple, can bloom all year round, flowering for 2-3 months.
basic.blooming: Flowers year around with spathe flower, viewing period 2-3 months
basic.color: Leaf color a mixture of dark green and pale green, bract pure white

maintenance.soil: Peat covered with a layer of sphagnum moss on soil surface to keep moisture
maintenance.sunlight: Like half shade, should put in places with bright scattered light
maintenance.watering: Likes wet environments, water thoroughly when soil is dry, may spray water in the air or on leaves, reduce water in winter, keep soil moist
maintenance.fertilization: Dilute fertilizers following instructions, apply 1-2 times monthly
maintenance.pruning: Remove rotten roots, old diseased and dead leaves timely
